      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "The much-anticipated debut of TREASURED LEGACY (10) is upon us, with the Peters Investments filly looking very impressive at the trials coming into this. She hasn't trialled since December, but her work has been very impressive. This doesn't look an overly strong 2YO race and she can start her career on the perfect note. DIVINE MIRAGE (9) is another debutant, with her trial form around the impressive Aurum Belle who won last week. Should get plenty of favours from the inside draw for Brad Parnham who hops on board. Can put her best foot forward on debut. ACE SNIPER (8) showed good improvement into her last trial at Lark Hill and looks ready for her debut. Fiore takes the ride and if she can run up to her recent trial, she won't be far away. DIXIE DOO (6) flew home a fortnight ago and the rise in trip looks ideal. Can be in the finish. MARCOS (4) has shown glimpses at the trials and is not to be discounted.",
